====================================================
STRICT HIERARCHY (MANDATORY)
====================================================

The system must strictly enforce the following hierarchy:

Product
 └── Application
      └── Project
           └── Task
                └── Finding

Rules:
- Products are top-level entities.
- Applications belong to a Product.
- Projects belong to an Application.
- Tasks belong to a Project.
- Findings belong to a Task.
- No entity may exist outside its parent.
- UI navigation and database relationships must strictly follow this hierarchy.

