====================================================
CRITICAL TEMPLATE LOCKING RULE
====================================================

This is a mandatory business rule.

When a Project is created:

Project
- Template Assigned = Template A
- Template Locked = True

Then:

All Tasks under that Project
All Findings under those Tasks

must inherit Template A.

Restrictions:

If Project Template Locked = True:

- Project template cannot be changed.
- Task template cannot be changed.
- Finding template cannot be changed.
- New tasks must inherit project template.
- New findings must inherit project template.

Users may edit data entered through the template.

Users may NOT modify template assignment.

Template locking must be enforced at:
- UI level
- API level
- Database validation level

